Awal-agi d awal n tideț yuklalen ad ițwaqbel ɣer yemdanen imi d-iḥyan si ger lmegtin.
Elset irkasen, meɛna ur țțawit ara yid-wen aqenduṛ wis sin. Qqimet deg yiwen uceṭṭiḍ-nni, dɣa acerrig-nni ad innerni.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lbaṭel, yesɛa amkan di lǧețța-s yerna yessamas.
Daymi i wen-qqaṛeɣ tura : ur țțaǧat ara abrid i wen-d-țwaceggɛem ayen akk ideṛṛun di mkul amkan agi, aț-țemyezwaǧet di mkul amkan amek ara tfehmem deg umeslay-nwen.
Eɛni ur tefhimem ara ayen bɣiɣ a wen-t-id-iniɣ ? Ilaq aț-țeẓrem acḥal n tikkal i kkun-ițmeslayem ɣef temdint n Ṛuma ?
Ger wid yellan yid-es, yiwen ur yefhim acuɣeṛ i s-yenna ayagi, meɛna ur ɛqilen ara kan s tutlayt ur nețwassen ara.
Deg ussan-nni, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa yețzid irennu. At Isṛail i d-yusan si tmura nniḍen, yețmeslayen s tyunanit, ccetkan ɣef wat Isṛail neɣ di tmurt n Maṣeṛ.
Akken daɣen, ur nceɛɛel ara taftilt iwakken a ț-nɣumm s kra, meɛna a ț-nessers ɣef lmeṣbeḥ, iwakken aț-țfeǧǧeǧ i tudrin n tmurt ara d-yasen.
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ur ilaq ara ad țḥawalent tissit n ccṛab meɛna ilaq ad nehhunt ɣer wayen yelhan,
Lɛid i deg xeddmen wat Isṛail tiɛecciwin iqeṛṛeb-ed ɣer temdint n Lquds, ițțin-ed i d-yusan si tmurt n Yahuda armi d ass n lɛid n wass wis xemsin.
Yekker-ed yiwen usennan s wayes i s-țmețțat ara s lexṣaṣ ; ṣubben seg umkan-nni iwumi yețwarfed ɣer igenni.
Di temdint n Jafa, ameqqran n tejmaɛt i d-yețwaɛfan i lɛeskeṛ iwakken ad sɛun amkan ; ma d nețța, a ten-yeǧǧa tamdint n Lquds akk-d wid nniḍen i gzedɣen di tmurt n Yahuda.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla asteqsi, mbla ma tḥebbṛem, aț-țedṛu yid-sen d yiwen.
M'ara k-id-yeɛreḍ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, m'ara temsalin, a d-bdun mbla cceḥḥa ;
Akken daɣen, Semɛun s yiman-ik yennejmaɛ-ed deg-s aṭas, acḥal i sen-yewɛeṛ lexbaṛ, ur tezmirem ara aț-țenɛețțabem sennig n tejmaɛt.
Ilaq-awen aț-țețbeggneḍ ɣer tegnawliw, a wen-d-yefk daɣen tiɣaltin uqbel ad iṛuḥ ; ma d kunwi, a wen-iṣubbeɣ lxedma-s, m'ara yili tafat n igenni tucmiț, ț-țaɛeggṛen i yiman-nwen.
Kra iɛeqqayen nniḍen ṛuḥen armi ț-țigzirt n Qubṛus, anda i gesteɛfagen lejdud-nneɣ Sidna Ibṛahim, Isḥaq, Yeɛqub akk-d wid n tilawin iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi.
Qellbet amek ara tɛeddim lɛid n Tuffɣa ara t-id-yawin ɣer temdint n Kafernaḥum. Yeɣli-d yakan lameṛ ɣer Qiṣarya, mačči ɣef lḥakem n wat Isṛail iqeṛben ɣuṛ-es, meɛna urɛad i d-yusi.
Akken daɣen i glaq ad yaɣ awal i Sidi Ṛebbi deg imi i d-yekkan aɛessas.
Akken daɣen i t-nezzenzem ɣer tigzirt n Luirin, iqleb-aɣ ɣer tama nniḍen ț-țamurt n wuzzal deg iḍaṛṛen, s ssnasel deg ifassen, meɛna m'ara țțazzalen ɣer tewwurt iwakken a t-yawi waḍu ɣer wanda yebɣa.
