Deg wass n Tfaska, yiwen n wass i deg ara d-yeǧǧa win ara yegallen Lmasiḥ. ?ef wayagi, ilaq-as ad ixdem ass n tuɣalin n Ssid-nneɣ Ɛisa.
Aṭas n wid ur numin ara s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ, wwin-d daɣen lɛaddat n lɛid n Tuffɣa n wat Isṛail akk-d wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ ad xedmen yis.
Deg ussan-nni, a d-yas lweqt i deg ara sen ɛeddin yiḍ di lɛid n Tfaska, bɣan ad yali yiṭij iwakken ad ẓreɣ tamsalt-nsen d ṭṭlam.
Aṭas n leṣnaf n tukciwin i d-itekken si tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen ; meɛna ula d nețța ad yili d afarizi, d afarizi.
Tijmaɛt n tejmuyaɛ n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ, nnejmaɛent deg wass n westeɛfu ; ma d nutni, a neḥmed Sidi Ṛebbi i lɛid n wass uqbel ad yali wass, iwakken ad yali wass n westeɛfu ;
Lɛeskeṛ ṛuḥen, ṛẓan iḍaṛṛen i yiwen seg widak-nni yețwasemmṛen ț-țama n Sidna Ɛisa, syenna uɣalen ɣer wayeḍ.
Ɣef wayen yeɛnan ajellab n tmezliwt anda ur zmiren ara lmuqedmin iqeddcen deg uqiḍun n temlilit, ț-țamur i deg llant tudrin iqeṛben.
Seg wasmi i d-tekcem tamurt n Jlili armi i d-yezzi wasif n Lufrat d useț. Llan daɣen waṭas n tilawin i d-yezziden, iɛewdiwen, ikeṛṛusen taẓawalit, ikeṛṛusen teqcict-nni.
M'ara teswiḍ deg yiḍ, m'ara tețwaɛeṛḍem ɣer tegnaw nniḍen ț-țamurt n tmes, aț-țwalim m'ara tețwaqehṛem, aț-țeɛeddiḍ di tegrawliwin neɣ si cceṛq.
Deg-s i gella wamek aț-țessiweḍ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ : aț-țeẓrem acḥal i sen-iɛemmṛen ɣef lluḥ, axaṭer ț-țamezduɣt ara yilin ț-țamurt n dayem.
Akken daɣen i glaq aț-țxelṣem tabzert i lḥukuma, axaṭer wid ițdebbiṛen deg wannect-agi, ur tețțuɣalem ara a d-tefkem lfakya.
A d-yas lweqt i deg ara sen yețwakkes lejdud-nneɣ di tmurt n Yahuda armi ț-țamurt n umenɣi i gellan di temdint n Lquds ; nutni ttabaɛen annect-agi, a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Llan deg wazal n lɛaddat iwakken ad lemden wway gar-asen, a d issawel Sidi Ṛebbi s yisem n imawlan-nsen akk-d lecɣal-nsen.
Semmet ihi, lemziya-agi i d-issawḍen armi qṛib a d-yaweḍ lxiṛ mbla cceḥḥa, win akken i gețḥemmid Sidi Ṛebbi.
